message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with the application of deep learning and machine learning techniques to detect rare pathologies in fundus photographs. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) domains. Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging and healthcare, which could also place it under the medical imaging (cs.MED) category. The use of t-SNE visualization tool and convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests a possible connection to the neural networks (cs.NEURON) category.
